of amazing tablets to bring you convenient, innovative features all packed into a slim and sexy profile. the note 3 offers to all users a larger and better screen for the best viewing experience and more powerful multitasking. coming also with the note 3 is the amazing s pen, sporting significant improvements that make your note 3 experience even better than ever before. large 5.7' full hd screen style too.  my magazine customise your very own layout with all your favourite apps, news updates, social media all neatly displayed to you in one organised page for your perusal. the dynamic presentation allows you easy and fast access to all you most used apps saving you tons of time – plus it looks great on the full hd screen too!  air command the most notable upgrade for note 3 can be seen in the new s pen. the s pen boasts revolutionizes the classic note-taking experience by providing the ability to accomplish everyday tasks with just a click. it plays an integral role in how users interface with the device, making all daily routines easier.  with the s pen, users are introduced to air command, a palette of five powerful features that takes your note 3 experience to the next level. a simple click of the s pen while hovering over the screen is all needs to open air command and with it you can toggle between screens, memorize commands or look different menus. the air command feature provides access to the following key functions: action memo the action memo feature enables users to handwrite a note and automatically execute a function or convert the handwritten content into a formatted content. furthermore, action memo can instantly initiate a call, add contacts, search an address on a map, search the web and so much more – the perfect multitasking tool.  scrapbook don't stress anymore about organizing the information and contents stored in your phone. with the scrapbook feature, you can organize and track down content and information from various sources including the web, youtube and gallery all in one place. just circle the information or image that you want to save and move it into scrapbook – it’s just that easy!  screen write the screen write feature captures the full screen image of the current page on the device and allows users to write comments or additional information onto the captured image. whether you’re having fun with doodling on the image or just writing a comment, it’s all up to you!  s finder searching for information that you want has never been easier with the s finder. the feature allows users to search for any content on their device and all the way to the web as well. just key in keywords or filters such as date, location and content and users will be presented with the results all displayed in one place.  pen window pen window allows users to use the s pen not only for drawing sketches or writing notes, but now also for opening a small application window for a true multitasking experience. simply by drawing a window of any size, anywhere on the screen, users can easily and quickly open another application window such as youtube, calculator or browser without pausing current activity on
